page.title: 18Kenny Carter
page.content: KENNY CARTERS FIRST NAME IS KENNETH MALCOM CARTER AND HES TWENTY FOUR YEARS OLD AND IS MARRIED TO PAMELA CARTER. THEY HAVE TWO CHILDREN NAMED KELLY MARIE AND MALCOM ROBERT KENNY CARTER. KENNY LIVES ON THE OUTSKIRTS OF HALIFAX. HE OWNS TWO SPEEDWAY BIKES AND A SPECIAL KENNY CARTER VAN. HES WON THE BRITISH CHAMPION SPEEDWAY TWO TIMES RUNNING,KENNY STARTED RACING WHEN HE WAS SIXTEEN YEARS OLD AND AT THE END OF EVERY YEAR HE EARNS LOTS OF MONEY. KENNY NOW HAS HUNDREDS OF TROPHIES AND DOESNT MIND ANYONE ASKING FOR HIS AUTOGRAPH. KENNY HAS HIS OWN FAN CLUB AND COSTS 1.95 TO JOIN A YEAR AND IN THAT YEAR YOU RECEIVE A BIRTHDAY AND OTHER THINGS SUCH AS MEMBERSHIPS.
